TRANSCENDENT : Fallen King

Role: Damage Dealer

Template: Component

1) Combat Style: The Foil

1. Foil: High raw damage

2. Épée: Damage + Slow effect

3. Sabre: Damage + Stun effect

2) Abilities

Super – Fallen Comet: Unleashes AoE spikes. Slows enemies instead of stunning.

Hypercharge – Dramatic Entrance: AoE stun on all nearby enemies upon entry. Optional damage burst; can buff summons from Commanding Lead

3) Passives

Stun Resistance: Crowd control resistance scales higher as the King's HP decreases

4) Gadgets

1. Spectral Chain: Pulls and drags enemies toward the King while dealing damage. Can also be used purely for damage without pulling.

2. Commanding Lead: Summons 3–5 Necrotic Skeletons to the battlefield

5) Star Powers

1. Bone Armor: For every 33% HP lost, the King gains a 10% damage reduction buff

2. Épée Overload: Enemies hit by the Épée stance no longer suffer a slow, but instead take significantly increased damage from all sources

6) Buffies

1. Gadget Buffie – Spectral Might

1.1. Spectral Chain: +25% pull speed, +15% damage

1.2. Commanding Lead: Summons 1 extra Necrotic Skeleton; +20% HP to all summons

2. Star Power Buffie – Royal Ascendancy

2.1. Bone Armor: +15% damage reduction per 20% HP lost

2.2. Épée Overload: Immobilizes enemies for 1 second; applies for every attack, not just Épée stance

3.Hypercharge Buffie – Comet’s Fury

Fallen Comet: +40% AoE size, +30% spike damage, each spike leaves a 2-second lingering burn
